# Security

- Redact secrets before any external provider call
- Never log raw prompts by default (`FUSION_LOG_RAW_PROMPTS=false`)
- MCP orchestration tools must not execute hidden shell commands or modify repo files
- Claude Code may still edit files and run commands normally after using Fusion output
- Do not commit `.env` files or API keys
- Deterministic checks must flag secret leakage in responses
